Tom Lester https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tom_Lester 0 Thomas William Lester (born September 23, 1938) is an American actor and evangelist, best known for his role as Eb Dawson, farmhand to Oliver Wendell Douglas (played by Eddie Albert) on the television series Green Acres. He appeared in two feature animal films, Gordy and Benji.
